metadata.name: Pepe family in the park
metadata.description:
This artwork inspired from "In the Park at the Chateau des Clayes"  by Edouard Vuillard.
I redrawn it mixed watercolor and old brush to keep the impressionism style.

The atmosphere of this painting is very amazing. So I would like to put Pepe family into it.
I want to show how they are relax and calm.
Can you feel it?

Digital art
Size : 5000 x 4000 PX
300 DPI

By YUKAN
